v20260416
=========

Major Updates
-------------

* client: Add Windows Terminal Client (client/main.py)
  - Thin client architecture with HTTPS + SSE streaming
  - Login/authentication with in-memory token storage
  - Session management (start/end) with timeout support
  - Streaming response output
  - Approval request handling

* build: Add test enforcement via git hooks (.githooks/)
  - pre-commit hook runs pytest before each commit
  - commit-msg hook enforces Linux kernel commit message format
  - Tests blocked from commit if any test fails

* build: Add unit tests for Client class (client/tests/)
  - 7 unit tests covering login, session, and auth flows
  - All HTTP calls mocked (no real network connections)

* docs: Reorganize documentation into skills/ directory
  - skills/client/CLAUDE.md
  - skills/gateway/CLAUDE.md
  - skills/orchestrator/CLAUDE.md

* build: Add development environment setup (setup.sh)
  - One-time repo setup script for git hooks and dependencies
  - client/requirements-dev.txt with pytest dependency

* build: Add .gitignore for Python cache files
